{"tid":1788342,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"2019聖誕交換禮物 (冇圖)","createTime":"2019-12-18T14:52:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T00:18:04.000Z","uid":198903,"like":55,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c5bf06b97cfd6ef58fdbb50584c7b259fcbe43d8","tid":1788342,"uid":198903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:52:01.000Z","msg":"嗱~聖誕節就到喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相信大家都煩緊買咩禮物好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等我比少少建議大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n通常交換禮物嘅Budget 都唔多，得個$50/$100，買份正經嘅禮物又唔夠錢，買啲伏野咩廁紙/牙膏/六合彩獎券嘅話，收到嗰個只會好無奈<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又浪費咗啲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以！！！！！！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n今年大家玩交換禮物🎁 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不如將啲錢拎去捐俾手足</span> 捐去星火又好點都好，幫下手足點都有意義過買啲唔等洗嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n集腋成裘，一人捐$50 $100，加加埋埋就好多架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家準備開心過聖誕嘅時候，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請唔好忘記有班手足俾人拉咗冇得同屋企人同朋友同另一半過冬過聖誕</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個聖誕大家儘量洗少啲錢啦，要食飯食聖誕大餐都記住去黃店食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n(第一次開po排版奇怪嘅話請見諒<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"4b20e63e19653023d92ade396cf58d40c293a553","tid":1788342,"uid":151539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:53:32.000Z","msg":"支持!<br />\n推"},{"pid":"411754b8acbc87c6ef41f8b41f34f35b7bacd7d0","tid":1788342,"uid":198903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:53:44.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"956dd47e40e326972c3313180776bf4f463c7a9e","tid":1788342,"uid":198903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:53:55.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"b5e30a8f0cb181c8f558ee08effbda535534cf2b","tid":1788342,"uid":198903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:54:07.000Z","msg":"自推3"},{"pid":"b97a48573dd1d095ff5cfd8dfb6f53266e613f47","tid":1788342,"uid":198903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:54:40.000Z","msg":"自推4"},{"pid":"f679ed3f99c5a1215082dfea9bf6d312bb769f68","tid":1788342,"uid":198903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:55:40.000Z","msg":"自推5"},{"pid":"1d7d89b9b1ede8110c4a9ea54794ef607f47f43f","tid":1788342,"uid":198903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:56:10.000Z","msg":"自推6"},{"pid":"0414d1c610e176f9585ae51482f9c0366f68e53a","tid":1788342,"uid":198903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:56:59.000Z","msg":"自推7"},{"pid":"9863557c2959d9fb4e7ba5e294673eef56d6473b","tid":1788342,"uid":198903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:57:44.000Z","msg":"自推8"},{"pid":"85c6551fabaf9e487d308a374cb169f0790fa8fa","tid":1788342,"uid":42360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:58:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e70a9653fa6fac604595013954fe9ff8da4f46d","tid":1788342,"uid":198903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T14:58:55.000Z","msg":"自推9"},{"pid":"b2eea19828b9b8bc5c8d34d97abf84678ef9161a","tid":1788342,"uid":198903,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"re